 <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n// n 은 0부터 시작한다. <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Zero-Based Numbering<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n// 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 4<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 6 ... 번째 형제 요소를 찾는다. <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>짝수 번째<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n// 0번째 요소라는 것은 없으므로 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 4번째 요소인 강아지<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 곰이 선택된다.</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.animals *:nth-child(2n + 1)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n// 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 5<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 7 ... 번째 형제 요소를 찾는다. <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>홀수 번째<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.animals *:nth-child(n + 2)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n// 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 4<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 5 ... 번째 형제 요소를 찾는다. <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>2번째 이후 요소<span class=\"token punctuat